The '''Indu Council''' was the governing body of the [[Indu San system/Legends|Indu San system]].

During a meeting on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Indu San/Legends|Indu San]] to discuss an alliance with the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], chief [[councillor]] of the Indu Council, [[Shek Barayel]], was assassinated by [[Council Authority]] [[Authority Officer|Officer]] [[Kaleb Darme]].

